<!-- ====================================================================== 
   El calentamiento es un <exploration> (distinto a las otras actividades)
   Para RRRRR usar el estilo del calentamiento. Por ejemplo, usar 
   RRRRRR=observa con los "Observa y Pregúntate"
===========================================================================  -->
<exploration xml:id="warm-observa-elNumDesconocido" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may notice:</p>
<ul>
      <li>The total in both diagrams is 128.</li>
      <li>There are 3 parts that have 8. This could be expressed as <m>3 \times 8</m>.</li>
      <li>There’s a question mark in the large section in one diagram, but a letter in the other.</li>
    </ul>
<p>Students may wonder:</p>
<ul>
      <li>Why does one have a question mark and one has the letter <m>b</m>?</li>
      <li>What problem could this diagram represent?</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


